	- Tuesday works for me.
		update polite_refuser_house03_jewish (relief)
		# UNSURE: "but briefly" frames the RV acceptance as visibly constrained —
		# polite but tired. Cast.md § 6.0.3 red line says no confrontation. Risk:
		# reads edge rather than constrained-polite. If playtest reads as edge,
		# swap to "Alright. Tuesday." (matches first_visit; sameness-of-response
